code: @Override public TypedValue getValueInternal(ExpressionState state) throws EvaluationException {     // Cache the concatenation of child identifiers     if (this.value == null) {         StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder().         for (int i = 0. i < getChildCount(). i++) {             Object value = this.children[i].getValueInternal(state).getValue().             if (i > 0 && (value == null || !value.toString().startsWith("$"))) {                 sb.append(".").             }             sb.append(value).         }         this.value = new TypedValue(sb.toString()).     }     return this.value. }

@Override public String toStringAST() {     StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder().     if (this.value != null) {         sb.append(this.value.getValue()).     } else {         for (int i = 0. i < getChildCount(). i++) {             if (i > 0) {                 sb.append(".").             }             sb.append(getChild(i).toStringAST()).         }     }     return sb.toString(). }
